  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "By integrating AI with blockchain technology, developers can create more secure and efficient Metaverse applications that offer a range of benefits for users and businesses alike, including increased trust, transparency, and privacy.",
    "Moreover, AI and blockchain can provide a platform for developing new and innovative use cases for the Metaverse, such as decentralized virtual marketplaces and secure digital identity systems.",
    "Blockchain is also essential to the growth of the Metaverse since decentralization is a key component of Web 3.0, the next generation of the web.",
    "Therefore, even Metaverse initiatives must be developed as decentralized platforms to support a decentralized web.",
    "Projects in the Metaverse can benefit from decentralization thanks to blockchain technology (Gadekallu et al. 2022)."
  ],
